-How old were you then?
-Old enough to know better.

288
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:02,992
And now that I think about it,
I stood in front of a case of iPods

289
00:14:03,199 --> 00:14:04,791
and I bought a Zune.

290
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,155
