you actually feel.

304
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,514
Because you'll either
be disappointed

305
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,278
or excited by the outcome.

306
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,435
Interesting.

307
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:51,712
So, heads it's PS4,
tails it's Xbox One.

308
00:14:53,199 --> 00:14:54,598
All right, I'll try.

309
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,909
What is it?

310
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:01,599
A quarter.

311
