I'm sorry. I can't do this.

317
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:29,152
My ex-girlfriend emailed me,
and I'm seeing her Saturday.

318
00:15:29,359 --> 00:15:31,589
And I'm glad you like it,
it's from J. Crew.

319
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,028
